'''亞柏·马科南·特斯法耶'''（{{lang-en|Abel Makkonen Tesfaye}}，{{lang-am|አቤል ተስፋዬ}}, ''{{transl|am|ʾÄbel Täsfaye}}''，1990年2月16日－），藝名'''威肯'''（{{lang-en|The Weeknd}}{{noteTag|1=音同「The Weekend」。}}），[[華語|華語]]圈綽號'''盆栽哥'''<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://m.66152.com/article/201904/3880.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2022-02-10 |archive-date=2022-02-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220210061352/https://m.66152.com/article/201904/3880.html }}</ref>、'''音樂魔人'''，是一名加拿大[[歌手|歌手]]、[[詞曲作家|詞曲作家]]、[[音樂製作人|音樂製作人]]及舞者。<ref name="sex-drugs">{{cite web|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/features/sex-drugs-and-r-b-inside-the-weeknds-dark-twisted-fantasy-20151021?page=6|title=Page 6 of Sex, Drugs and R&B: Inside The Weeknd's Dark Twisted Fantasy - Rolling Stone|author=|date=|work=Rolling Stone|accessdate=2015-11-01|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612143929/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/features/sex-drugs-and-r-b-inside-the-weeknds-dark-twisted-fantasy-20151021?page=6|dead-url=yes}}</ref>2010年末，特斯法耶上傳了一些歌曲至[[YouTube|YouTube]]並署名「威肯」(The Weeknd)。他在2011年發布三支內有九首歌的混音帶：《{{le|House of Balloons|House of Balloons}}》、《{{le|Thursday|Thursday (album)}}》、《{{le|Echoes of Silence|Echoes of Silence}}》，這些混音帶廣受好評。<ref name=happy>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/music/house-of-balloons/critic-reviews |title=House of Balloons – The Weeknd |publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate=2012-03-16 |archive-date=2021-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107223916/https://www.metacritic.com/music/house-of-balloons/critic-reviews |dead-url=no }}</ref>翌年，他發布了合輯《{{le|Trilogy|Trilogy (The Weeknd album)}}》，其由混合不同元素的三十首翻唱曲目以及三個額外的歌曲組成。此專輯是由[[聯眾唱片|聯眾唱片]]及[[XO_(唱片公司)|XO]]共同推出。

2013年，威肯推出了他的首張[[錄音室專輯|錄音室專輯]]《{{le|親親國度|Kiss Land}}》，主打歌為〈{{le|Kiss Land|Kiss Land (song)}}〉及〈{{le|Live For}}〉。他的第二張錄音室專輯《[[狂野之美|狂野之美]]》，成為他第一張登上[[公告牌二百强专辑榜|《公告牌》二百强专辑榜]]冠軍專輯。其中單曲〈{{le|值得 (威肯歌曲)|Earned It|值得}}〉登上了[[告示牌百強單曲榜|《告示牌》百強單曲榜]]前五名，〈[[山丘_(威肯歌曲)|山丘]]〉、〈[[無法擋的愛|無法擋的愛]]〉則登上了《告示牌》百強單曲榜第一名。上述單曲都同時在「《告示牌》熱門[[節奏藍調|節奏藍調]]歌曲榜」前三名，使得他成為史上第一位囊括「《告示牌》熱門藍調歌曲榜」前三名的歌手。<ref name=alone>[http://music.cbc.ca/#!/blogs/2015/7/Alone-on-the-podium-The-Weeknd-becomes-first-artist-to-take-over-Billboard-RB-chart "Alone on the podium: The Weeknd becomes first artist to take over Billboard R&B chart"] {{Wayback|url=http://music.cbc.ca/#!/blogs/2015/7/Alone-on-the-podium-The-Weeknd-becomes-first-artist-to-take-over-Billboard-RB-chart |date=20120212163426 }}. [[CBC_Music|CBC Music]], 17 July 2015.</ref>他曾經獲得兩座[[葛萊美獎|葛萊美獎]]，以及被[[奧斯卡最佳原創歌曲獎|奧斯卡最佳原創歌曲獎]]提名。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.grammy.com/artist/the-weeknd | title=The Weeknd | publisher=The Recording Academy | accessdate=2016-03-03 | archive-date=2017-04-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170419192514/https://www.grammy.com/artist/the-weeknd | dead-url=no }}</ref>2016年9月，威肯宣布將發行新專輯《[[星聞人物_(專輯)|星聞人物]]》，並釋出2支單曲：〈[[星聞人物_(歌曲)|星聞人物]]〉及〈{{le|錯愛|False Alarm (the Weeknd song)}}〉。<ref name=":0" />2019年11月，威肯回歸並釋出2支單曲〈[[Heartless|Heartless]]〉及〈[[Blinding_Lights|Blinding Lights]]〉。2020年2月，威肯公布新專輯名稱《[[黑潮時刻|黑潮時刻]]》（After Hours），且釋出一支專輯同名單曲，並宣布將在一個月後發行此專輯。2020年3月20日，新專輯《黑潮時刻》正式發行。<ref name="#1">{{cite news|language=en|author=Lisa Respers France|url=https://edition.cnn.com/2020/03/20/entertainment/weeknd-after-hours-trnd/index.html|title=The Weeknd releases 'After Hours'|publisher=CNN|date=2020-03-20|accessdate=2020-03-26|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120020730/https://edition.cnn.com/2020/03/20/entertainment/weeknd-after-hours-trnd/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>23日，威肯發行《黑潮時刻（豪華版）》。2022年1月7日驚喜釋出《[[黑潮時刻|黑潮時刻]]》的下一篇張《[[黎明FM|黎明FM]]》發行後，並在告示牌全球榜寫下新紀錄-成為單週史上男歌手最多，打入前200大紀錄一共24首歌。<ref>{{cite news|language=en|author=Carl Lamarre|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/hip-hop/9340445/the-weeknd-after-hours-deluxe|title=The Weeknd Releases 'After Hours' Deluxe Edition and There's an Appearance From Lil Uzi Vert|publisher=Billboard|date=2020-03-23|accessdate=2020-03-26|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120020737/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/hip-hop/9340445/the-weeknd-after-hours-deluxe|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==早年生活==
亞柏·马康南·特斯法耶（Abel Makkonen Tesfaye）<ref name="sex-drugs"/>生於1990年2月16日的[[加拿大|加拿大]][[安大略|安大略]][[士嘉堡|士嘉堡]]。<ref name=allmusic>{{cite web |url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/the-weeknd-mn0002674162/biography |title=The Weeknd Biography |first=Andy |last=Kellman |publisher=[[Allmusic|AllMusic.com]] |accessdate=2015-10-13 |archivedate=2015-10-13 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6cFl8uYyO?url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/the-weeknd-mn0002674162/biography |deadurl=no }}</ref>童年亦在該處成長。<ref name="jcaramanica">{{cite news |first=Jon |last=Caramanica |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/08/02/magazine/can-the-weeknd-turn-himself-into-the-biggest-pop-star-in-the-world.html?_r=1 |title=Can The Weeknd Turn Himself Into the Biggest Pop Star in the World? |work=[[The_New_York_Times_Magazine|The New York Times Magazine]] |date=2015-07-27 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6cFlDxFgo?url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/08/02/magazine/can-the-weeknd-turn-himself-into-the-biggest-pop-star-in-the-world.html?_r=0 |archivedate=2015-10-13 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2016-07-04 }}</ref>他是位[[獨生子|獨生子]]<ref name="RSinterview">{{cite web|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/features/sex-drugs-and-r-b-inside-the-weeknds-dark-twisted-fantasy-20151021?page=3|title=Sex, Drugs and R&B: Inside The Weeknd's Dark Twisted Fantasy|author=Josh Eeels|work=[[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]]|publisher=([[Wenner_Media_LLC|Wenner Media LLC]])|date=2015-10-21|accessdate=2015-11-11|archive-date=2018-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180622083831/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/features/sex-drugs-and-r-b-inside-the-weeknds-dark-twisted-fantasy-20151021?page=3|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。他擁有[[衣索比亞|衣索比亞]]血統。父母親马康南（Makkonen）及萨姆拉（Samra）在1980年代從衣索比亞移民至加拿大。<ref name="jcaramanica"/><ref name="RStone">{{cite web |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/features/sex-drugs-and-r-b-inside-the-weeknds-dark-twisted-fantasy-20151021 |title=Sex, Drugs and R&B: Inside The Weeknd's Dark Twisted Fantasy |date=2015-10-21 |access-date=2015-10-26 |archive-date=2018-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180615145745/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/features/sex-drugs-and-r-b-inside-the-weeknds-dark-twisted-fantasy-20151021 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Mistry">{{cite web |first=Anupa |last=Mistry |url=http://www.torontostandard.com/culture/daily-disc-the-weeknds-echoes-of-silence |title=Daily Disc: The Weeknd's 'Echoes Of Silence' |publisher=Torontostandard.com |accessdate=2012-12-30 |archive-date=2019-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191129110625/http://www.torontostandard.com/culture/daily-disc-the-weeknds-echoes-of-silence/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>他的母親曾經做過幾項工作包括護理，餐飲，夜校。<ref name="RSinterview"/>在特斯法耶長大的過程中，他父親就不在身邊了，他的母親時時刻刻在工作，他的祖母照料他大部分的青春歲月。因此，特斯法耶會說一口流利的[[阿姆哈拉語|阿姆哈拉語]]，這是他學會的第一種語言。<ref name="where the e went">{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1714103/the-weeknd-reddit-ama/|title=The Weeknd Reveals How He Got His Name... And Where The ‘E’ Went|work=MTV News|publisher=MTV|accessdate=2013-09-15|archive-date=2021-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210223071428/http://www.mtv.com/news/1714103/the-weeknd-reddit-ama/|dead-url=no}}</ref>他的祖母會帶他去[[衣索比亞正教會|衣索比亞正教會]]服務。<ref name="RSinterview"/>

特斯法耶自我描述了他的青少年时期的电影“孤立无援的儿童”("''KIDS'' without the [[AIDS|AIDS]]")。 特斯法说他11岁开始吸食大麻，他也声称他经常购買毒品以滿足他对摇头丸，羟考酮，阿普唑仑，可卡因，裸盖菇素和氯胺酮的依賴性。<ref name="jcaramanica"/><ref name="auto">{{cite web|last1=Wagstaff, Swanson|first1=Keith, David|title=10 Things You Should Know About the Weeknd|url=https://www.gq.com/story/5-things-you-should-know-about-the-weeknd|website=GQ|accessdate=2016-11-13|archive-date=2018-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180704214239/https://www.gq.com/story/5-things-you-should-know-about-the-weeknd|dead-url=no}}</ref>

特斯法耶說，他採用了藝名The Weeknd的由來是在17歲高中輟學之後，他與他的同儕在一個週末（weekend）時，在家人都不知道的情況下離家出走。他更改了weekend拼寫方式，以避免與加拿大樂團{{le|The Weekend|The Weekend (Canadian band)}}有商標上的問題。<ref name="jcaramanica"/><ref name="where the e went"/>

==事業生涯==
===2010-11：事業開始及混音帶===


特斯法耶在[[多倫多|多倫多]]遇見了一位製作人傑洛米·羅斯，他有一個「黑暗節奏藍調音樂計畫」的點子名為「The Weeknd」。在羅斯試圖將想法推銷給音樂家{{le|Curtis Santiago|Curtis Santiago}}之後，羅斯為特斯法耶彈奏了一小段曲子，而特斯法耶則即興的哼出了一段[[即興饒舌|饒舌]]，在這之後，他們開始製作一張專輯。他製作了三首歌曲：“What You Need”、“Loft Music”、以及“The Morning”，特斯法耶唱饒舌的部分，但是最後並沒有被羅斯採用。羅斯讓特斯法耶在「這三首歌曲要記功在羅斯上」的條件下保留他製作的歌曲。<ref name="McGuire">{{cite journal|last=McGuire|first=Patrick|date=April 2012|url=http://www.vice.com/read/how-the-producer-of-the-weeknds-breakout-tracks-got-majorly-screwed|title=How the Producer of The Weeknd’s Breakout Tracks Got Majorly Screwed|journal=[[Vice_(magazine)|Vice]]|location=New York|accessdate=2013-03-03|archive-date=2016-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161128105754/http://www.vice.com/read/how-the-producer-of-the-weeknds-breakout-tracks-got-majorly-screwed|dead-url=no}}</ref>然而，特斯法耶在2010年12月上傳了“What You Need”、“Loft Music”、以及“The Morning”至[[YouTube|YouTube]]，並署名「威肯」。<ref name="nytimes">{{cite news| last = Caramanica A-Train| first = Jon| url = http://www.nytimes.com/2011/01/02/arts/music/02playlist.html?_r=4&ref=music| title = Screams That Charmed, and Other Overlooked Highlights| work = [[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]| date = 2010-12-26| accessdate = 2011-03-29| archive-date = 2021-01-08| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210108025018/https://www.nytimes.com/2011/01/02/arts/music/02playlist.html?_r=4&ref=music| dead-url = no}}</ref>儘管他的身份最初是不被知道的。<ref name="pforkwynreview">{{cite web| last = Fitzmaurice| first = Larry| url = http://pitchfork.com/reviews/tracks/12131-what-you-need/| title = The Playlist – The Weeknd – ''What You Need''| publisher = [[Pitchfork_Media|Pitchfork Media]]| date = 2011-03-04| accessdate = 2011-03-29| archive-date = 2011-03-26| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110326174005/http://pitchfork.com/reviews/tracks/12131-what-you-need| dead-url = yes}}</ref><ref name="washpost">{{cite web| last = Stewart| first = Allison| url = http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2011/03/14/AR2011031403984.html| title = Singles File: Da Phuture, The Weeknd, Fever Ray| work = [[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]| date = 2011-03-14| accessdate = 2011-03-29| archive-date = 2020-11-30| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201130063156/https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2011/03/14/AR2011031403984.html| dead-url = no}}</ref>歌曲通過口耳相傳在網路上被注意到了，包括由多倫多歌手[[德瑞克_(歌手)|德瑞克]]在以發表歌曲為特色的部落格發布的文章。<ref name="McGuire"/>德瑞克對威肯產生了興趣。<ref>{{cite web|last=Escobedo Shepherd|first=Julianne|url=http://www.thirteen.org/riffcity/music/love-and-other-drugs-the-weeknds-altered-state-rb/|title=Love and Other Drugs: The Weeknd’s Altered-State R&B|publisher=[[WNET|WNET]]|date=2011-03-23|accessdate=2013-01-21|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129222613/https://www.thirteen.org/riffcity/music/love-and-other-drugs-the-weeknds-altered-state-rb/|dead-url=no}}</ref>他們隨後收到來自[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]及[[Pitchfork_Media|Pitchfork Media]]的報導。

2011年3月21日，特斯法耶透過他的網站免費地發布一張有九首歌曲的混音帶：《{{le|歡樂之屋|House of Balloons}}》。<ref name="mtv">{{cite web| last = Ramirez| first = Erika| url = http://rapfix.mtv.com/2011/03/21/say-hello-to-the-weeknd-drake-co-signs/| title = Say Hello to The Weeknd, Drake Co-Signs| publisher = MTV| date = 2011-03-21| accessdate = 2011-03-29| archive-date = 2015-10-12| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151012012132/http://rapfix.mtv.com/2011/03/21/say-hello-to-the-weeknd-drake-co-signs/| dead-url = no}}</ref>專輯由{{le|Doc McKinney|Doc McKinney}}及{{le|Illangelo|Illangelo}}出品，即使他上述的三首歌曲並沒有歸功於羅斯。<ref name="McGuire"/>《歡樂之屋》獲得了一致好評，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/music/house-of-balloons/the-weeknd|title=House of Balloons Reviews|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2013-03-03|archive-date=2020-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201105094556/https://www.metacritic.com/music/house-of-balloons/the-weeknd|dead-url=no}}</ref>它被{{le|2011年北極星音樂獎|2011 Polaris Music Prize}}提名為10位入圍提名人之一。<ref name=shortlist>{{cite web |url=http://www.polarismusicprize.ca/2011/ |title=Polaris Music Prize |author= |date= |work=Polaris Music Prize |accessdate=2015-11-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140409053023/http://www.polarismusicprize.ca/2011/ |archivedate=2014-04-09 }}</ref>

2011年7月，威肯開始踏上巡迴演唱的道路，他在多倫多的{{le|Mod Club|Mod Club Theatre}}開始了他的第一次演出。一個小時半的演出中製造了有關他的謠言。<ref>Ritchie, Kevin (25 July 2011). [http://www.nowtoronto.com/daily/music/story.cfm?content=181922 The Weeknd’s perfect premiere] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nowtoronto.com/daily/music/story.cfm?content=181922 |date=20111222100021 }}.''[[NOW_Toronto|NOW Toronto]]''. Retrieved 28 March 2012</ref>他下一個演出地點選擇在多倫多的{{le|莫爾森加拿大露天劇場|Molson Canadian Amphitheatre}}。他和饒舌歌手德瑞克共同合作並且以特別嘉賓的身分於同年7月31日出席德瑞克第二個{{le|OVO音樂節|OVO Fest}}。<ref>{{cite web|last=Fitzmaurice|first=Larry|date=2011-07-03|url=http://pitchfork.com/news/42716-the-weeknd-to-play-drakes-ovo-festival/|title=The Weeknd to Play Drake's OVO Festival|publisher=Pitchfork Media|accessdate=2011-03-27|archive-date=2021-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107223855/https://pitchfork.com/news/42716-the-weeknd-to-play-drakes-ovo-festival/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在夏天時，媒體意識到威肯拒絕被採訪並選擇透過[[Twitter|Twitter]]與外界溝通。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Melody Lau |date=2011-07-25 |title=Mysterious R&B singer sells out first show |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/drake-protege-the-weeknd-proves-hes-no-fluke-in-live-debut-20110725#ixzz1sE1WqJ6N |journal=[[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]] |location=New York |accessdate=2012-03-16 |archive-date=2017-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171208231547/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/drake-protege-the-weeknd-proves-hes-no-fluke-in-live-debut-20110725#ixzz1sE1WqJ6N |dead-url=no }}</ref>他的第二張混音帶《{{le|星期四 (專輯)|Thursday (album)|星期四}}》於2011年8月18日釋出，該專輯可以從威肯的網站免費下載，並且受到評論家的好評。<ref name=npost>Dunlevy, T’Cha (23 March 2012). [http://arts.nationalpost.com/2012/03/20/365-days-of-weeknd-we-chart-abel-tesfayes-rise-to-fame-a-year-after-house-of-balloons/ "365 days of Weeknd: We chart Abel Tesfaye’s rise to fame a year after House of Balloons"] {{Wayback|url=http://arts.nationalpost.com/2012/03/20/365-days-of-weeknd-we-chart-abel-tesfayes-rise-to-fame-a-year-after-house-of-balloons/ |date=20141113205034 }} .''[[National_Post|National Post]]''. Retrieved 27 March 2012</ref>威肯的第三張混音帶《{{le|深幽回音|Echoes of Silence}}》於2011年12月21日釋出。<ref name=npost/><ref>The Weeknd's Official site [http://the-weeknd.com/ Official Site] {{Wayback|url=http://the-weeknd.com/ |date=20200317025203 }}. Retrieved 28 March 2012</ref>2011年釋出的三個混音帶被統稱為「氣球三部曲」，<ref>{{cite web| url= http://thelineofbestfit.com/news/latest-news/echoes-of-silence-the-weeknd-reveals-final-part-of-the-balloons-trilogy-77249| title= Echoes Of Silence The Weeknd reveals final part of the Balloons Trilogy The Line Of Best Fit| date= 2011-12-22| publisher= theLineofBestFit.com| accessdate= 2013-10-20| archive-date= 2020-09-19| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200919013537/https://www.thelineofbestfit.com/news/latest-news/echoes-of-silence-the-weeknd-reveals-final-part-of-the-balloons-trilogy-77249| dead-url= no}}</ref>並都備受好評，也增長了特斯法耶的粉絲團。<ref name="Kellman"/>

===2012-14：《三部曲》及《親熱國度》===

2012年4月，威肯在[[科切拉音樂節|科切拉音樂節]]表演，開始了他在[[美國|美國]]的巡迴演唱會。<ref name="tour">{{cite web |url=http://pitchfork.com/news/46157-watch-the-weeknds-entire-coachella-set/?utm_medium=site&utm_source=more-of&utm_name=news |title=Abel Tesfaye makes his U.S. debut |author=Snapes, Laura |date=2012-04-16 |publisher=Pitchfork Media |accessdate=2012-03-16 |archive-date=2020-09-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200922090700/https://pitchfork.com/news/46157-watch-the-weeknds-entire-coachella-set/?utm_medium=site&utm_source=more-of&utm_name=news |dead-url=no }}</ref>他和他的樂隊造訪各個主要城市，<ref name="tour"/>最後在[[紐約|紐約]]結束了他的巡演。[[滾石_(雜誌)|滾石雜誌]]給予在紐約兩場票售罄的演唱會正面的評價。<ref name="Stones">{{cite journal |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/the-weeknd-mesmerizes-at-bowery-ballroom-20120429 |title=The Weeknd Mesmerizes at Bowery Ballroom |author=Krishnamurthy, Sowmya |journal=Rolling Stone |location=New York |date=2012-04-29 |accessdate=2012-05-27 |archive-date=2012-05-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120526210653/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/the-weeknd-mesmerizes-at-bowery-ballroom-20120429 |dead-url=no }}</ref>特斯法耶和他的巡迴樂團繼續在[[歐洲|歐洲]]各個主要的[[音樂節|音樂節]]巡演，包括在[[西班牙|西班牙]]和[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]]的{{le|春天之聲音樂節|Primavera Sound Festival}}、<ref>{{cite web |url=http://prettymuchamazing.com/news/the-weeknd-announces-first-ever-tour |author=Luis Tovar |title=The Weeknd announces first ever tour |publisher=prettymuchamazing.com |accessdate=2012-03-16 |archive-date=2019-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191130204832/https://prettymuchamazing.com/news/the-weeknd-announces-first-ever-tour |dead-url=no }}</ref>在[[英國|英國]][[倫敦|倫敦]]的{{le|無線音樂節|Wireless Festival}}、<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.wirelessfestival.co.uk/line-up/ |title=Wireless line up 2012 |publisher=wirelessfestival.co.uk |accessdate=2012-03-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120316180853/http://www.wirelessfestival.co.uk/line-up/ |archivedate=2012-03-16 }}</ref>還有在[[法國|法國]][[巴黎|巴黎]]及[[比利時|比利時]][[布魯塞爾|布魯塞爾]]的演唱會。他在英國首站倫敦表演時，在觀眾面前翻唱[[麥可·傑克森|麥可·傑克森]]的歌曲“[[Dirty_Diana|Dirty Diana]]”，其中[[凱蒂·佩芮|凱蒂·佩芮]]及[[芙蘿倫絲·威爾希|芙蘿倫絲·威爾希]]也在臺下聆聽。<ref name="June">{{cite journal |url=http://www.nme.com/news/weekend--3/64204 |title=The Weeknd covers Michael Jackson as he plays his debut UK show |journal=[[NME|NME]] |location=London |accessdate=2012-12-30 |archive-date=2013-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029210302/http://www.nme.com/news/weekend--3/64204 |dead-url=no }}</ref>六月時，根據報導，「氣球三部曲」已被下載800萬次，這將在今年晚些時候正式發布。<ref name="June"/>

