在2012年9月，威肯簽約[[Republic_Records|Republic Records]]，並且在其旗下創立[[唱片公司|唱片公司]]品牌[[XO_(唱片公司)|XO]]。<ref name="Hampp">{{cite journal|last=Hampp|first=Andrew|date=2012-11-12|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/the-juice/474219/the-weeknd-reps-talk-clearing-samples-touring-for-trilogy-release|title=The Weeknd & Reps Talk Clearing Samples, Touring For 'Trilogy' Release|journal=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|location=New York|accessdate=2012-11-17|archive-date=2013-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130306002619/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/the-juice/474219/the-weeknd-reps-talk-clearing-samples-touring-for-trilogy-release|dead-url=no}}</ref>合輯《{{le|三部曲 (專輯)|Trilogy (The Weeknd album)|三部曲}}》於同年11月釋出，它是由混合不同元素的三十首翻唱曲目以及三個額外的歌曲所組成。<ref name="pitchfork.com">{{cite web| url= http://pitchfork.com/news/48066-the-weeknd-shares-rolling-stone-video-trilogy-artwork| title= The Weeknd Shares 'Rolling Stone' Video, Trilogy Artwork| publisher= [[Pitchfork_Media|Pitchfork Media]]| accessdate= 2012-12-30| archive-date= 2020-12-04| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201204002441/https://pitchfork.com/news/48066-the-weeknd-shares-rolling-stone-video-trilogy-artwork/| dead-url= no}}</ref>此合輯也正式地將《{{le|歡樂之屋|House Of Balloons (The Weeknd mixtape)}}》的三首歌曲歸功羅斯於製作人及作者。<ref>{{cite AV media notes|title=[[Trilogy_(The_Weeknd_album)|Trilogy]]|others=The Weeknd|year=2012|type=CD liner notes|publisher=[[Republic_Records|Republic Records]]|id=3719793}}</ref>《三部曲》登上[[加拿大專輯榜|加拿大專輯榜]]第五名及[[美國|美國]][[告示牌200大專輯榜|告示牌200大專輯榜]]第四名，並於第一週賣出8萬6千張。<ref name="bb">{{cite web|url={{BillboardURLbyName|artist=The weeknd|chart=all}}|title=Trilogy — The Weeknd|work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|publisher=[[Prometheus_Global_Media|Prometheus Global Media]]|accessdate=2012-11-23}}</ref><ref name="Caulfield">{{cite journal|last=Caulfield|first=Keith|date=2012-10-10|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/474052/one-direction-tops-billboard-200-chart-twilight-debuts-at-no-3|title=One Direction Tops Billboard 200 Chart, 'Twilight' Debuts at No. 3|journal=Billboard|location=Los Angeles|accessdate=2012-11-21|deadurl=no|archive-date=2015-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925094740/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/474052/one-direction-tops-billboard-200-chart-twilight-debuts-at-no-3}}</ref>不久後在12月，[[英國廣播公司|英國廣播公司]]公布威肯已經被[[年度新聲|2013年度新聲]]提名。<ref name="so13">{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p010q6bc/profiles/theweeknd|title=Sound of 2013 Profiles: The Weeknd|publisher=BBC|date=2012-12-09|accessdate=2012-12-10|archive-date=2012-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121213061703/http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p010q6bc/profiles/theweeknd|dead-url=no}}</ref>2013年5月，《三部曲》被[[美國唱片業協會|美國唱片業協會]]認證為[[RIAA認證|白金唱片]]且被[[加拿大音樂協會|加拿大音樂協會]]認證為雙重白金唱片。<ref name="RIAA">{{cite web|url=http://www.riaa.com/goldandplatinumdata.php?artist=%22THE%20WEEKND%22|title=Gold & Platinum Searchable Database|publisher=[[Recording_Industry_Association_of_America|Recording Industry Association of America]]|accessdate=2012-12-19}}{{dead link|date=February 2016}}</ref><ref name="MC">{{cite web |url=http://www.musiccanada.com/GPSearchResult.aspx?st=Trilogy&sa=The+Weeknd&smt=0 |title=Gold and Platinum Search |publisher=[[Music_Canada|Music Canada]] |accessdate=2012-12-21 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130927064324/http://www.musiccanada.com/GPSearchResult.aspx?st=Trilogy&sa=The+Weeknd&smt=0 |archivedate=2013-09-27 }}</ref>

2013年5月16日，威肯首次演出他首張錄音室專輯《{{le|親熱國度|Kiss Land}}》之主打歌“{{le|Kiss Land (歌曲)|Kiss Land (song)|Kiss Land}}”，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.complex.com/music/2013/05/listen-the-weeknd-kiss-land|accessdate=2013-05-17|title=Listen: The Weeknd "Kiss Land"|last=Nostro|first=Lauren|date=2013-05-16|archive-date=2020-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124205738/https://www.complex.com/music/2013/05/listen-the-weeknd-kiss-land|dead-url=no}}</ref>他說本專輯將會於9月10日釋出。<ref>{{cite web|last=Williott|first=Carl|date=2013-07-22|url=http://idolator.com/7472491/the-weeknd-kiss-land-release-date-cover-artwork|title=The Weeknd Unveils ‘Kiss Land’ Release Date & Cover Artwork|publisher=[[Idolator_(website)|Idolator]]|accessdate=2013-07-22}}</ref>這張專輯也推出與[[德瑞克_(歌手)|德瑞克]]合作的歌曲“Belong to the World”及“{{le|Live For|Live For}}”，並且在九月開始了「威肯秋季巡迴演唱會」。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thisgoesin.com/2013/07/the-weeknds-kiss-land-arrives-on-august-27th-belong-to-the-world-snippet-news/ |title=The Weeknd’s ‘Kiss Land’ Arrives on August 27th, "Belong To The World" Snippet |date=2013-07-13 |publisher=ThisGoesIn |accessdate=2013-07-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130723110346/http://www.thisgoesin.com/2013/07/the-weeknds-kiss-land-arrives-on-august-27th-belong-to-the-world-snippet-news/ |archivedate=2013-07-23 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.amazon.com/Live-For-feat-Drake/dp/B00EP54R5U|title=Amazon.com: Live For [feat. Drake] [Clean]: The Weeknd: MP3 Downloads|publisher=|accessdate=2015-03-11|archive-date=2020-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200821060400/https://www.amazon.com/Live-For-feat-Drake/dp/B00EP54R5U|dead-url=no}}</ref>《親熱國度》得到了音樂評論家的普遍好評。<ref name="metacritic1">{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/music/kiss-land/the-weeknd |title=Kiss Land Reviews |publisher=Metacritic |date= |accessdate=2013-09-09 |archive-date=2015-05-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150528001038/http://www.metacritic.com/music/kiss-land/the-weeknd |dead-url=no }}</ref>《親熱國度》空降美國[[告示牌200大專輯榜|告示牌200大專輯榜]]第二名，賣出9萬6千張，只比當週排名第一的[[齊斯·艾本|齊斯·艾本]]專輯《{{le|Fuse (專輯)|Fuse (Keith Urban album)|Fuse}}》少賣2千張。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5695587/keith-urban-edges-the-weeknd-for-no-1-debut-on-billboard-200 |title=Keith Urban Edges The Weeknd for No. 1 Debut on Billboard 200 |publisher=Billboard |date=2012-12-01 |accessdate=2013-09-19 |archive-date=2015-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151106214849/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5695587/keith-urban-edges-the-weeknd-for-no-1-debut-on-billboard-200 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

