==個人生活==

[[貝拉·哈蒂德|貝拉·哈蒂德]]在2015年初開始與威肯約會，這對情侶第一次被看到在一起是該年四月的[[科切拉音樂節|科切拉音樂節]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/style-blog/wp/2015/09/11/kylie-jenner-and-bella-hadid-are-18-their-boyfriends-are-25-why-do-their-relationships-elicit-such-different-reactions/|title=Kylie Jenner and Bella Hadid are 18. Their boyfriends are 25. Why do their relationships elicit such different reactions?|date=2015-09-11|author=Soraya Nadia McDonald|work=Washington Post|accessdate=2015-10-17|archive-date=2015-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150929220636/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/style-blog/wp/2015/09/11/kylie-jenner-and-bella-hadid-are-18-their-boyfriends-are-25-why-do-their-relationships-elicit-such-different-reactions/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.elle.com/culture/celebrities/a31091/bella-hadid-19th-birthday/|title=Bella Hadid Spends Her Birthday Weekend With The Weeknd|author=Sarah Lindig|work=ELLE|accessdate=2015-10-17|archive-date=2015-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151011190536/http://www.elle.com/culture/celebrities/a31091/bella-hadid-19th-birthday/|dead-url=no}}</ref>哈蒂德在2015年12月主演他的歌曲“{{le|In the Night|In the Night (The Weeknd song)}}”之[[音樂錄影帶|音樂錄影帶]]。在2016年2月的葛萊美頒獎典禮上，情侶倆在紅地毯上亮相。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.popsugar.com/celebrity/Weeknd-Bella-Hadid-Grammys-2016-40199219#photo-40199219|title=The Weeknd and Bella Hadid Made Their Red Carpet Debut at the Grammys|last=Sisavat|first=Monica|website=POPSUGAR Celebrity|language=en-US|access-date=2016-06-06|archive-date=2016-05-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160530144852/http://www.popsugar.com/celebrity/Weeknd-Bella-Hadid-Grammys-2016-40199219#photo-40199219|dead-url=no}}</ref>2016年11月，有報導聲稱貝拉和威肯分手，但也有消息表示他們依然戀愛中，只是行程有過多的衝突。<ref>{{cite web|last1=TRACY|first1=BRIANNE|title=The Weeknd and Bella Hadid Have Split: 'They Still Have a Great Deal of Love for One Another'|url=http://people.com/music/the-weeknd-bella-hadid-split/|website=People|publisher=Time INC.|date=2016-11-10|accessdate=2017-04-09|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210223041118/https://people.com/music/the-weeknd-bella-hadid-split/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2016年年底，威肯被狗仔拍到和[[席琳娜·戈梅茲|席琳娜·戈梅茲]]兩人在餐廳外熊抱擁吻，公開戀情，而貝拉也取消對席琳娜在[[Instagram|Instagram]]的追蹤。2017年年底，威肯和席琳娜·戈梅茲分手，而威肯也取消對席琳娜在[[Instagram|Instagram]]的追蹤。

他在社交媒體上，例如[[Twitter|Twitter]]，將他的名字後方加上「xo」作為字尾。<ref name="Hoby"/>根據Hermione Hoby的敘述，它的意思是{{le|擁抱與親吻|Hugs and kisses|一個親吻與一個擁抱}}的表情符號，<ref name="Hoby">{{cite news|last=Hoby|first=Hermione|date=2012-11-08|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/music/2012/nov/08/the-weeknd-sense-and-sensibility|title=The Weeknd: Sounds and sensibility|newspaper=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|location=London|at=section G2, p. 12|accessdate=2013-01-06|archive-date=2013-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130707160659/http://www.guardian.co.uk/music/2012/nov/08/the-weeknd-sense-and-sensibility|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[VH1|VH1]]的Zara Golden說，它用來代替使用消遣性毒品[[搖頭丸|搖頭丸]]，{{le|羥考酮|Oxycodone}}及[[氯胺酮|氯胺酮]]。<ref>{{cite web|last=Golden|first=Zara|date=2012-11-16|url=http://www.vh1.com/music/tuner/2012-11-16/who-is-the-weeknd-5-things-you-should-know|title=Who Is The Weeknd? 5 Things You Should Know|publisher=[[VH1|VH1]]|accessdate=2013-08-16|archive-date=2013-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130127024250/http://www.vh1.com/music/tuner/2012-11-16/who-is-the-weeknd-5-things-you-should-know|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

