2015年1月，威肯由於毆打拉斯維加斯警察而被逮捕。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Stutz|first1=Colin|title=The Weeknd Arrested For Punching Las Vegas Police Officer|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/the-juice/6436581/the-weeknd-arrested-for-punching-las-vegas-police-officer|website=Billboard|accessdate=2016-08-08|archive-date=2021-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208014251/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/the-juice/6436581/the-weeknd-arrested-for-punching-las-vegas-police-officer|dead-url=no}}</ref>他並沒有為他的行為辯護，並被判處50小時的社區服務。<ref>{{cite web|title=THE WEEKND Pleads No Contest TO PUNCHING A COP|url=http://www.tmz.com/2015/10/22/the-weeknd-no-contest-punching-cop/|website=TMZ|accessdate=2016-08-08|archive-date=2021-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107224114/https://www.tmz.com/2015/10/22/the-weeknd-no-contest-punching-cop/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

